，为他们提供更高的工作灵活性，以便在遇到恶劣天气、突发情况或需要兼顾家庭事务时，可自行决定在效率最高、最舒适的地方工作。 「快乐工作，认真生活」 是阿里巴巴力倡的企业文化之一，员工福利方案在业内向来颇具竞争力，比如 2011 年即率先推出员工免息贷款置业计划、补充商业保险和其他保障项目；阿里员工父母每年可享受免费 「康乃馨」 体检服务。 今年 7 月，在原有保障的基础上，阿里又进一步为员工及其子女新增百万医疗保险，同时将员工免息购房贷款额度提升至 80 万元。此外，阿里花样翻新的餐厅、健身房等丰富园区配套也一直深受职场年轻人欢迎。消息称阿里员工福利再升级，将全面试行灵活办公及新增育儿假 - IT 之家"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b6a6da874600891fec31b63de2450b60_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/503495910"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3u/Ug63XwuYsEAMaCDc0MTY5MTEwIOiwqI0GMBw4mgZAE3IJNTAzNDk1OTEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1638671226.199032", "card_id": "Q_502336820", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "a 岛的动物园怪谈为什么能火起来？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/502336820"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3u/Ug63XwuYsEAMaCDczOTExNzQzIPHYkI0GMAI4gAFAFHIJNTAyMzM2ODIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1638671226.1993387", "card_id": "Q_493632517", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 264}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "我想知道一个女生怎么才能保持不恋爱脑？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/493632517"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3u/Ug63XwuYsEAMaCDcxOTc3MzM5IKSPw4sGMAM4igNAFXIJNDkzNjMyNTE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1638671226.1995723", "card_id": "Q_442904528", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1230}, "target": {"title_area": {"